            :tags   #{"damage" "survivability"}}
           {:effect "You and your undead minions gain +1 necrotic damage for a minute (stacking) whenever you cast a Necromancy spell."
            :tags   #{"damage" "magic"}}
           {:effect "You and your undead minions are proficient in Constitution saving throws while concentrating on a non-cantrip Necromancy spell."
